item.dc:creator: @ApocalypseX ApocalypseX
item.description:
@ApocalypseX wrote:

Ahhhhh. Alright. Here’s what you got to do.
Go to Start Menu (Press Windows button/Start button)
Go to Computer RIGHT CLICK and hit Properties.
Environmental Variables.
Delete your PATH/CLASSPATH in System Files/User Files.

Donedone.
If it doesn’t work, tell me.
